@{
    Layout = "_Layout";
}
@*
    _ViewStart.cshtml — runs before every Razor Page in this folder and subfolders.
    Sets the default layout so each page doesn't have to declare it manually.

    The framework looks for _Layout.cshtml in Pages/Shared/ (then Views/Shared/ as fallback).

    Same role as the MVC Views/_ViewStart.cshtml — nothing changes here.
*@
